        "name": "Innate Spellcasting",
        "text": "[name]'s innate spellcasting ability is Charisma (spell save DC sdc[cha]). [name] can innately cast the following spells, requiring no material components:\n\nAt will: *darkness*, *invisibility*\n1/day each: *charm person*, *cone of cold*, *gaseous form*, *sleep*"
